description:
*The Black Panther Deception* | The movie, _Black Panther,_ was a worldwide blockbuster success, ranking as one of the top movies of all time! In this documentary, our friend, Isaac Olatunji Jr., PhD (affectionately known as Dr. O.), explores the movie plot, themes, and characters from a biblical perspective, uncovers the hidden and not-so-hidden spiritualism in the film, and discusses why we shouldnt be exposing ourselves to such content.
